nodes.text: Sunset Prayer of the Guardians of the Whills

The Sunset Prayer of the Guardians of the Whills was a prayer recited at dusk by the Guardians of the Whills, a Force-worshipping organization from Jedha. The prayer's provenance was uncertain, but a copy recovered from the outskirts of Jedha City was archived under the file name "Document #JP0103."
